  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Forklift & Stacker Driver",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Duties & Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Operate Reach Truck</li><li>Operate Forklift</li><li>Unloading cargo from incoming vehicles and stacking them to assigned places</li><li>Scanning Cargo</li><li>Moving cargo to pallets for storage</li><li>Identify damage and report shortage of cargo</li><li>Count physical inventory and maintain inventory control</li><li>Weekly/monthly stock check</li><li>To highlight to supervisor any problems encountered in the course of their duties</li><li>Comply with company policies and guidelines</li><li>Assist in keeping a safe working environment</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Must possess a reach truck license</li><li>Regularly lift and/or move objects</li><li>Experience as a reach truck operator is required</li><li>Singaporean/Singapore PR only </li></ul><p><u><strong>Working Hours</strong></u></p><ul><li>5.5-day work week</li><li>Mon – Fri: 8.30am – 5.30pm</li><li>Sat: 8.30am – 12.30pm</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Benefits</strong></u></p><ul><li>Opportunity for OT</li><li>Positive & friendly work environment</li></ul><p><u><strong>Performance Standards</strong></u></p><ul><li>No complaints from direct superior</li><li>Good communication, organization and time-management skills</li><li>Reliable employee</li><li>Good attitude and cooperation (teamwork)</li><li>Be initiative and a team player.</li></ul><p>Interested applicants may call 62662234 (EXT: 111) to schedule an interview.</p>",
