    "description": "<p>Founded in 1996, Kang Logistics started as a purely warehousing company, providing storage solutions to various companies. We have grown to provide services of full container trucking as well as providing last mile deliveries. Currently, we are working with big companies such as Kuehne &amp; Nagel (KN).</p>\n<p>We have a large fleet of vehicles ranging from vans to 10ft and 24ft lorries, to Prime Movers.</p>\n<p>Kang Logistics is a member of Singapore Logistics Association and we have accreditation with ISO &amp; Bizsafe.</p>",
